# ScheduleActions(date, dayCount)
- IF: ${ dayCount == 1 }
    - ```
    {
        "type": "ActionSet",
        "actions": [
            ${CreateEventAction(date)},
            ${GetEventsAction(addDays(formatDateTime(date), 1))}
        ]
    }
    ```
- ELSE: 
    - ```
        {
        "type": "ActionSet",
        "actions": [
            ${CreateEventAction(date)}
        ]
    }
    ```